            <a href="/" class="text-primary font-weight-bold">Manage Manufacturers</a> <br>
            Maintain the list of drug manufacturers and whether they offer patient assistance programs (PAP).
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-4 p-1">
